@startuml
actor User
participant "Datastream\n(Cross-Dock Pipeline)" as Pipeline
database "Cloud Storage\n(Cross-Dock Bucket)" as Bucket
participant "Cloud Function\n(Cross-Dock Publisher)" as Publisher
participant "TMS Bridge" as TMSBridge
database "TMS Database" as TMSDB
participant "CALSuite" as CALSuite

User -> TMSDB: Data Change on SEN_TS
Pipeline -> TMSDB: Listen for Changes (Transaction Logs)
Pipeline -> Bucket: Store CDC Event
activate Bucket
Bucket -> Publisher: Trigger on new file
activate Publisher

Publisher -> TMSBridge: Read Transport Orders (HTTPS)
activate TMSBridge
TMSBridge -> TMSDB: Read Transport Orders (TCP/IP)
activate TMSDB
TMSDB -> TMSBridge: Return Transport Orders (Result Set)

deactivate TMSDB
TMSBridge --> Publisher: Transport Order Data (JSON Response)
deactivate TMSBridge

note right of TMSBridge
  Potential Bottleneck:
  - Processing delay (1-3 sec)
  - Sequential dependencies
  - Limited concurrency
end note

Publisher -> CALSuite: Publish Events (Azure Service Bus)

Publisher --> Bucket : Acknowledge Processing
deactivate Publisher
deactivate Bucket
@enduml